                           <desc>Unidentified text concerning the history of the Near and Middle
                              East under the Turkish rule.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           
                           <note> Carefully written. The text may be a piece from the second part of
                              the “History of Walda ʾAmid” concerning the history of Islam.</note>
                        </item>
